---
import Projects from "../components/Projects.astro";
import Technologies from "../components/Technologies.astro";
import Timeline from "../components/Timeline.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<Layout title="Kadeem Lewis">
  <main>
    <section class="opening">
      <section id="intro">
        <h1>
          Hi! üëãüèø My name is <span>Kadeem Lewis</span> and I turn ideas into code.
        </h1>
      </section>

      <section class="socials">
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kadeemlewis/"
          target="_blank"
          aria-label="linkedin link"
        >
          <Icon name="mdi:linkedin" />
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/kadeem-lewis"
          target="_blank"
          aria-label="github link"
        >
          <Icon name="mdi:github" />
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://www.reddit.com/user/kadeemlewis/"
          target="_blank"
          aria-label="reddit link"
        >
          <Icon name="mdi:reddit" />
        </a>
        <a
          href="mailto:email@kadeemlewis.com"
          target="_blank"
          aria-label="email address link"
        >
          <Icon name="mdi:email" />
        </a>
      </section>
    </section>
    <div class="resume-button-container">
      <button class="resume-button">
        <a href="/KadeemLewisResume.pdf" target="_blank">View my Resume</a>
      </button>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <section id="about">
      <h2>About Me</h2>
      <p>
        The first website I ever tried to make was in 2019 for a videogame I
        played. I didn't know anything about code so I tried learning Wordpress
        to build the site. I wasn't able to finish building the site but through
        the process, I realized that this was something I enjoyed.
      </p>
      <p>
        Since then I have learned much more than Wordpress and my passion for
        this field is just as high as it was the day I centered my first div. I
        have used these skills that I have acquired to contribute to my personal
        projects, excel in my classes and even contribute to a startup. I hope
        to be able to use and continue to improve my skills in future endeavors!
      </p>
    </section>
    <hr />
    <section>
      <h2>Skills</h2>
      <Technologies />
    </section>
    <hr />
    <section id="experience">
      <h2>Experience</h2>
      <Timeline />
    </section>
    <hr />

    <section id="projects">
      <h2>Projects</h2>
      <Projects />
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
  main {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  section {
    scroll-margin-top: 4rem;
  }
  #intro {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      span {
        color: hsl(var(--primary));
      }
    }
  }
  .opening {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .socials {
    display: flex;
    justify-self: end;
    gap: 2rem;
    [data-icon] {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
  .resume-button-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .resume-button {
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 2px solid hsl(var(--border));
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: auto;
    background-color: hsl(var(--background));
    &:hover {
      scale: 1.05;
      transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }
    a {
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .socials {
      justify-self: center;
    }
  }

  [data-icon] {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
</style>
